@taymourheikal 

`get_league()` and `get_league_entry()` take in a list of summoner ids. You're passing it a string which (since strings are iterable) the code assumes is a list of single digit ids which is why if you look at the results that you get - you'll probably notice some single digit ids in there

Pass in `'65593898'` as a list `['65593898']` to those methods and it should work

